":65074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"跌吉班仆街成日話跌15%會掃貨架<br />\n好快俾佢地托返高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013bb17fd46683ad266275f6d98e257b1f039e54","tid":879523,"uid":34286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"32adaa6ea77fbed32ce2a613237bca987feb19a0","tid":879523,"uid":6211,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"班淡友日日j個別成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵個屋苑整體跌一成既例子黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"香港12年來首度加息，至今剛「滿月」。期間樓市明顯轉差，綜合地產代理數據，全港起碼有14個大型指標屋苑在加息後平均樓價報跌，當中有6個屋苑的跌幅更達雙位數。<br />\n<br />\n指標屋苑實用呎價回落，其中，九龍灣德福花園繼早前成交價已跌至「5字頭」。香港置業譚征稱，該屋苑現時平均實用呎價12,866元，較加息前驟跌逾17%。同區的上車熱門屋苑得寶花園實用呎價15,583元，亦急跌超過12%。"},{"pid":"9c22f8c71eb400fd9c6ecfb123f4d1f007977380","tid":879523,"uid":37599,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32adaa6ea77fbed32ce2a613237bca987feb19a0","tid":879523,"uid":6211,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"班淡友日日j個別成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵個屋苑整體跌一成既例子黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"近30日最大跌幅成交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/173139_94d6bce3eda5b982ee6efe3f03896abf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F173139_94d6bce3eda5b982ee6efe3f03896abf.png&h=29f6c2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼埋近30日最大升幅成交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/173341_6e2fe3ae8328aff8c72a0f30b7cc7775.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F173341_6e2fe3ae8328aff8c72a0f30b7c